claim.claim-text:
A method for increasing resistance to citrus canker disease in a plant or cell, comprising
(a) transforming a plant or cell with a construct comprising at least one nucleotide sequence set forth in SEQ ID NO: 2-13, operably linked to a promoter active in plant cells;
(b) regenerating a plant from said transformed plant or cell;
(c) selecting a plant or cell that has increased resistance to citrus canker disease relative to a control plant.
